Let's just subtract all of the
w vectors from both sides of

00:09:00.100 --> 00:09:01.900
this equation.

00:09:01.900 --> 00:09:02.880
So what are we going to get?

00:09:02.880 --> 00:09:09.990
We're going to get c1, v1
plus c2, v2 all the

00:09:09.990 --> 00:09:13.975
